Volkswagen’s Audi June Sales Rise 19% to 117,650 Vehicles

-- B y   R a j i v   S e k h r i
-- 
2011-07-07T09:00:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-07/volkswagen-s-audi-june-sales-rise-19-to-117-650-vehicles.html
Volkswagen AG (VOW) ’s Audi luxury-car
division said sales rose 19 percent in June to 117,650 vehicles,
the Ingolstadt, Germany-based company said in an e-mailed
statement today.  German sales rose 18 percent from the year-earlier period,
the carmaker said. Unit sales climbed 121 percent in Brazil and
29 percent in  China , including Hong Kong.  “The first half of the year went better than we expected,”
Audi marketing and sales chief Peter Schwarzenbauer said in the
statement. “We are also optimistic for the coming months.”  To contact the reporter on this story:
Rajiv Sekhri in Frankfurt at 
